  <abstract id="abstr_chi" date-changed="20091227" lang="chi" format="original">
    <p num="1">该自行车中轴里侧装与内接链轮相咬合的从动轮和同轴装的离合轮，离合轮以链条连接飞轮。为1∶5的高速档。外侧装链轮以链条连接飞轮。为1∶3的低速档。离合轮一侧有牙嵌，另一侧装换档叉与车前换档杆相连，以子柄滑动在母柄导槽中的活动曲柄，在工作部分，子柄被牵引轮推出，曲柄伸长，在空转部分，子柄被拉回，曲柄缩短。牵引轮由内外两圈组成，内圈固装在立管与下管上，外圈有轮咀与子柄相连，随子柄旋转，它起着偏心轮作用，带动子柄在母柄导槽中伸出缩回。</p>
  </abstract>
  <abstract id="abstr_eng" date-changed="20091227" lang="eng" format="original">
    <p>The utility model relates to a two-gear bicycle with larger and smaller two chains and the inner side of the middle axis of the bicycle is provided with a driven wheel being articulated with an inner chain wheel and a clutch wheel with the same axis, wherein, the clutch wheel is connected with flywheels through chains and the inner side is a 1: 5 high-speed gear. The outer side of the middle axis is provided with chain wheels to connect the flywheels by chains as a 1: 3 low-speed gear. One side of the clutch wheel is provided with a jaw and the other side is provided with a gear-shifting fork which is connected with a gear-shifting bar. An auxiliary handle slides at the movable crank of the groove of a main handle, so in operation the auxiliary handle is pushed out by a traction wheel and the crank is extended while in spinning the auxiliary handle is pulled back and the crank is shortened. The traction wheel is composed of an inner and an outer cycles, wherein, the inner cycle is fixed on a standpipe and a lower pipe and the outer cycle is provided with a wheel nozzle to be connected with the auxiliary handle. The traction wheel is rotated along the auxiliary handle and has the role of an eccentric wheel to drive the auxiliary handle to extend and retract from the groove of the main handle.</p>
  </abstract>
